title: Jason Derulo to perform live at Dubai World Cup 2026 on March 28
summary_full: Dubai World Cup 2026 is set to be a grand affair with pop star Jason Derulo headlining the post-race concert on March 28.  The event boasts $30.5 million in prize money and promises a spectacular celebration following the world's richest race day. Tickets are now available, including concert access.
